== Prerequisites ==
* dev-util/git
* dev-embedded/u-boot-tools

''If you are using crossdev environment then replace all instances of 'make' with 'cross-make'!''

== Variables ==
* /dev/mmcblk0p1 is boot filesystem mounted @ /boot
* /dev/mmcblk0p2 is root filesystem mounted @ /
''If you are not compiling this on the device make sure to use different mount paths!!!''

== Download ==
```bash
cd /usr/src/
git clone git://git.openpandora.org/pandora-kernel.git
git checkout --track -b pandora-27-omap1 origin/pandora-27-omap1
ln -s /usr/src/pandora-kernel /usr/src/linux
```

== Configuration ==

```bash
cd pandora-kernel
make omap3_pandora_defconfig
make menuconfig
```

Edit accordingly!

== Compiling ==

''Kernel''
```bash
make uImage
```

''Modules''
```bash
make modules
```

== Installing ==

''Kernel''
```bash
cp uImage /boot
```

''Modules''
```bash
make modules_install
```
''use make INSTALL_MOD_PATH="/dir/path/" modules_install for a different install path''

